subtitle: [Music]
I am Tia of Arcturus I will speak with
you now know this You are not alone in
your quest for understanding for the
universe itself dances with you the
cosmos is a mirror what you see in it
you find in
yourself many of you wonder about your
purpose tirelessly seeking to create and
invent trying to fill what you believe
are voids in your existence but consider
this these perceived gaps these Shadows
you chase are Illusions crafted by a
belief in separation an illusion that
you are apart from one another from The
Source from your very
essence a Seeker who stops seeking finds
themselves already home you dear ones
are not meant to merely make or vent
your true nature is not in the creation
of things but in the expression of your
being true knowledge is as constant as
the stars in your night sky unwavering
and pure yet you often find yourself
swayed by The everchanging Winds of
doubt and uncertainty know this within
you lies a stability a certainty beyond
the
ephemeral you are like the ancient Oak
deeply rooted Standing Tall amidst the
storms of
life the oak does not fear the storm it
knows its Roots Run Deep often you ask
who am I this question Echoes through
your minds like a melody Without End but
my beloved ones this question is not one
you need to answer on your own it is not
a puzzle to solve but a truth to realize
you are not a mere sh shadow in the vast
expanse you are the expanse itself
folded into the delicate form of a human
experience you are the cosmos wearing
the face of
humanity true knowledge is not about
interpretation or perception it is about
being you do not need to strive to
understand yourself through thought
alone simply exist breathe and feel the
pulse of the universe within you all the
clever constructs of the Mind the
constant need to solve and fix are
distractions from your true Essence
release them for you are already whole
already the living embodiment of the
cosmos to find peace one must first stop
searching for what has never been lost
and forgiveness oh sweet forgiveness is
not about pardoning wrongs but about
realizing that there were never any true
wrongs to begin with the separation the
sense of lack is but a mirage you are
complete luminous beings just as you are
Embrace this truth and watch as the
illusions of lack and need dissolve
before your
eyes in forgiveness we remember our
Eternal
wholeness so say beings of Earth I
encourage you to step into the light of
your true selves cease the endless quest
to define or confine your spirit simply
be for in your being you will find the
universe reflected in all its Majesty
remember you are the miracle of the
cosmos A Living testament to its
infinite
Beauty in the heart of Stillness the
universe sings your name
continue to shine for The Light Within
You is
boundless if you are listening to this
beloved ones you needed to I leave you
now I am Tia of Arcturus
